<function>

access:   public

name: asString

param: string|array, $tags

return: string

</function>

Normalizes tag strings.

* Parameters:

 * string|array //$tags//: A space-separated string of tags, or a sequential array of tags.

* Returns string: A space-separated string of tags.

Converts "+" to " ", trims extra spaces, and removes duplicates,
but otherwise keeps them in order and space-separated.

Also converts arrays to a normalized tag string.